author: Quint Forgey
title: Trump: 'LIBERATE' states with Dem-issued stay-at-home orders
description: The president's social media posts come amid growing frustration among some in conservative circles over the stay-at-home orders.
content:
President Donald Trump. | Alex Brandon/AP Photo
